    title: 'Private-label branding & retail-ready packaging for your knitwear',
    description:
      'How a blank tee becomes your brand: woven vs printed labels, neck prints, hang tags, poly bags, barcodes, and retail-ready packaging — plus the artwork a factory needs and how custom trims affect MOQ and lead time.',
